onder if Mapper has fewer internals compared to a default converter list. I also need to check if the XStream constructor still sets up Mappers and the ReflectionProvider. Maybe it still includes the classLoaderReference and mapper chain. I'm also considering existing errors with converters like DatatypeFactory and TimeZone that could be in the converter list. There's a lot to untangle here!\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Figuring out converters**\\n\\nI’m thinking it might not be strictly required to create those converters, but I want to test it out first. It could be worth adding the necessary imports. I definitely need to create some minimal converter classes for this project. Let’s take a moment to inspect the methods in the interfaces, so I can see what I’m working with and how to approach the implementation efficiently. This feels like a logical next step!\"}]}"}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_U2AhkFPV4qysLbFBbG1CodCQ|fc_0cf34db58f3bc8f60169f00d51ec98819f8d7b52b1a2915ee5", "name": "bash", "arguments": {"command": "rg -n \"interface ConverterLookup|interface ConverterRegistry|interface SingleValueConverter|class StringConverter\" /home/vjovanov/c/forge2/metadata-forge/local_repositories/source_context/com.thoughtworks.xstream/xstream/1.4.20/main/extracted -S", "timeout": 10}}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_DjnriWOUI3ze7watWKwAdRlb|fc_0cf34db58f3bc8f60169f00d51eca8819f897f69a4bd59aac0", "name": "read", "arguments": {"path": "/home/vjovanov/c/forge2/metadata-forge/local_repositories/source_context/com.thoughtworks.xstream/xstream/1.4.20/main/extracted/com/thoughtworks/xstream/converters/ConverterLookup.java", "limit": 80}}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_EzxfCZIKXOdfbCLctaXJQNPr|fc_0cf34db58f3bc8f60169f00d51ecb0819fa6175707a346aadd", "name": "read", "arguments": {"path": "/home/vjovanov/c/forge2/metadata-forge/local_repositories/source_context/com.thoughtworks.xstream/xstream/1.4.20/main/extracted/com/thoughtworks/xstream/converters/Converter